text: Hakeem Abdul-Saboor (born November 7, 1987) is an American bobsledder. He competed in the two-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:American male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of the United States Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
